---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="The Seagull's Journey — May">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>The Seagull's Journey</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">
      Essays on transition, clarity, decisions, and real life. Written
      while I'm in the middle of the process myself.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Reflections -->
  <section class="posts-section narrow">
    <div class="section-label">
      <h2>Reflections</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Longer pieces about what remained after the dust settled.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="posts-list">
      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/vergonha-da-primeira-versao">
          <h2>a vergonha da primeira versão</h2>
          <p>If you look back and feel proud of the first version, you took too long to ship.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/dont-try-harder">
          <h2>if whatever you're doing isn't working, don't try harder</h2>
          <p>On stopping the self-blame when the plan fails — and changing the plan.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/como-foram-suas-ferias">
          <h2>como foram suas férias?</h2>
          <p>On how we lost the habit of telling stories and started sharing instants.</p>
          <span class="date">july 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/maquina-do-tempo-das-avos">
          <h2>a máquina do tempo das avós</h2>
          <p>A quiet luxury just for me and for them.</p>
          <span class="date">july 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/the-war-of-art">
          <h2>the war of art</h2>
          <p>On the Resistance — the force that keeps us from pursuing what matters.</p>
          <span class="date">july 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/a-gaivota">
          <h2>a gaivota</h2>
          <p>About my father, the thermals, Pedra da Gavea, and the tattoo that binds us.</p>
          <span class="date">june 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/o-que-fazer-com-a-minha-vida">
          <h2>o que fazer com a minha vida?</h2>
          <p>Understand, dream, prototype, live. A framework for building your life with intention.</p>
          <span class="date">june 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item">
        <a href="/escrita/carta-para-o-eu-do-futuro">
          <h2>carta para o eu do futuro</h2>
          <p>Analyze with perspective, your life is long.</p>
          <span class="date">june 2023</span>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fragments -->
  <section class="posts-section narrow">
    <div class="section-label">
      <h2>Fragments</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">What remained before becoming thought — fragments, signals, almost-poems.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="posts-list">
      <article class="post-item fragment">
        <a href="/escrita/wind-waves-roar">
          <h2>wind. waves. roar.</h2>
          <p>On intensity, wonder, and the smell of sea spray.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item fragment">
        <a href="/escrita/the-track">
          <h2>the track</h2>
          <p>I don't know where I'm going but I know how to get there.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item fragment">
        <a href="/escrita/ubuntu">
          <h2>ubuntu</h2>
          <p>I am; therefore, we are.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="post-item fragment">
        <a href="/escrita/integrity-cleanse">
          <h2>integrity cleanse</h2>
          <p>White belt, blue belt, black belt. A path of truth with yourself.</p>
          <span class="date">november 2024</span>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 5rem auto 4rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .page-sub {
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    line-height: 1.7 !important;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .posts-section {
    padding: 0 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-label h2 {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 0.88rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-muted) !important;
  }

  .posts-list {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .post-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .post-item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .post-item a {
    display: block;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .post-item a:hover h2 { color: var(--accent); }

  .post-item h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .post-item p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .date {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }
</style>
